public class RegexBlockTaglet
extends ParamBlockTaglet

Regular expression block taglet.

This taglet uses the RegexParamTextFilter to perform the text filtering.

In addition to the SimpleRegexBlockTaglet this taglet supports all features of the ParamBlockTaglet and therefore automatically creates definition lists.
